'''葡萄糖酸锌'''（[[化学式|化学式]]：C<sub>12</sub>H<sub>22</sub>O<sub>14</sub>Zn）是[[锌|锌]]的[[葡萄糖酸|葡萄糖酸]][[盐_(化学)|盐]]，是一种[[离子化合物|离子化合物]]，由[[锌|二价锌离子]]和[[葡萄糖酸|葡萄糖酸根]]构成，多见于[[膳食补充剂|膳食补充剂]]中，用以补充[[锌元素|锌元素]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://pubchem.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/compound/443445|title=Zinc gluconate|first=|last=PubChem|website=pubchem.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.trivenichemical.com/gluconate2.html|title=Zinc Gluconate Compound,Ferrous Gluconate Compound,Zinc Gluconate Chemical,Ferrous Gluconate Chemical|website=www.trivenichemical.com}}</ref><ref name="webmd">{{cite web|url=https://www.webmd.com/vitamins/ai/ingredientmono-982/zinc|title=Zinc: Uses, Side Effects, Interactions, Dosage, and Warning|website=www.webmd.com}}</ref>。

== 制备方法 ==
葡萄糖酸锌可经由[[葡萄糖酸|葡萄糖酸]]与[[氧化锌|氧化锌]]或[[乙酸锌|乙酸锌]]反应来制得<ref>{{Literatur |Autor=Hui Feng, Zhiwei Xu, Qianfeng Li, Xiuru Wang, Qiuyue Song |Titel=One pot synthesis, characterization and mechanism of zinc glycinate monohydrate |Verlag= |Ort= |Datum=2015-05-30 |Seiten= |DOI=10.2991/asei-15.2015.420}}</ref>。

== 物化性质 ==
葡萄糖酸锌呈白色结晶或粉末，易溶于[[水|水]]，不溶于[[有机溶剂|有机溶剂]]。葡萄糖酸锌可以[[水合物|水合物]]形式存在，最高可形成三水合物<ref name="George A. Burdock">{{Literatur |Autor=George A. Burdock |Titel=Encyclopedia of Food and Color Additives |Verlag=CRC Press |Datum=1997 |ISBN=978-0-8493-9414-0 |Seiten=2999 |Online=https://books.google.de/books?id=NtaR9i3hYCYC&pg=PA2999#v=onepage&q&f=false}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|author=Sumitra Ramachandran, Pierre Fontanille, Ashok Pandey and Christian Larroche|title=Gluconic Acid: A Review|journal=Food Technology and Biotechnology|volume=44|issue=2|pages=185–195|year=2006|url=http://www.ftb.com.hr/44/44-185.pdf|accessdate=2006-12-06|archive-date=2018-03-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180311100244/http://www.ftb.com.hr/44/44-185.pdf|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|author=Henk G.J. de Wilt|title=Part I: The oxidation of Glucose to Gluconic Acid|journal=Ind. Eng. Chem. Prod. Res. Develop.|volume=11|issue=4|page=370|year=1972|doi=10.1021/i360044a002}}</ref>。

== 药用 ==
葡萄糖酸锌作为[[锌化合物|锌化合物]]，可用于预防或治疗[[鋅缺乏|锌缺乏症]]<ref name="webmd"/>。
[[世卫组织|世卫组织]]建议在用于缓解[[腹泻|腹泻]]引起的[[脱水|脱水]]症状的{{tsl|en|oral rehydration solution|口服补液}}配方中加入葡萄糖酸锌
<ref name="WHOrec">W. U. Khan, D. W. Sellen: [http://www.who.int/elena/titles/bbc/zinc_diarrhoea/en/ ''Zinc supplementation in the management of diarrhoea''], WHO April 2011</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://rehydrate.org/zinc/index.html|title=Zinc and other micronutrients - Diarrhoea, Diarrhea, Dehydration, Rehydration - Rehydration Project|website=rehydrate.org}}</ref>。葡萄糖酸锌等锌盐也用于预防或治疗[[感冒|感冒]]<ref>{{cite journal|url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/9612589/|title=Zinc gluconate and the common cold. Review of randomized controlled trials|first=S.|last=Marshall|date=1998-05-01|publisher=|journal=Canadian Family Physician Medecin De Famille Canadien|volume=44|pages=1037–1042|via=PubMed|pmid=9612589|pmc=2277668}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/6367635/|title=Reduction in duration of common colds by zinc gluconate lozenges in a double-blind study|first1=G. A.|last1=Eby|first2=D. R.|last2=Davis|first3=W. W.|last3=Halcomb|date=1984-01-01|publisher=|journal=Antimicrobial Agents and Chemotherapy|volume=25|issue=1|pages=20–24|via=PubMed|doi=10.1128/aac.25.1.20|pmid=6367635}}</ref>。一项以两种[[安慰剂|安慰剂]]为[[对照实验|对照]]的[[雙盲|双盲研究]]表明，服用葡萄糖酸锌[[片剂|片剂]]可将感冒症状的严重程度降低约40%，并使病程缩短三到四天，但常产生[[胃肠道|胃肠道]][[副作用|副作用]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.efsa.europa.eu/fr/efsajournal/pub/1113 |title=Europäische Behörde für Lebensmittelsicherheit: ''Wissenschaftliches Gutachten: Nahrungsergänzungsmitteln für Ernährungszwecke zugesetztes Chrompicolinat, Zinkpicolinat und Zinkpicolinatdihydrat.'' |accessdate=2020-08-17 |archive-date=2013-08-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130810145734/https://www.efsa.europa.eu/fr/efsajournal/pub/1113 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="DOI10.7326/0003-4819-125-2-199607150-00001">Sherif B. Mossad: ''Zinc Gluconate Lozenges for Treating the Common Cold.'' In: ''Annals of Internal Medicine.'' Nr. 125, 1996, S. 81, [[doi:10.7326/0003-4819-125-2-199607150-00001|doi:10.7326/0003-4819-125-2-199607150-00001]].</ref><ref name="PMID1397668">J. C. Godfrey, B. Conant Sloane, D. S. Smith, J. H. Turco, N. Mercer, N. J. Godfrey: ''Zinc gluconate and the common cold: a controlled clinical study.'' In: ''The Journal of international medical research.'' Band 20, Nummer 3, Juni 1992, S. 234–246, {{ISSN|0300-0605}}, PMID 1397668.</ref>。

根据1998年发表的一项以小儿为实验对象的研究，[[片剂|片剂]]形式的葡萄糖酸锌对小儿[[普通感冒|普通感冒]]没有明显的缓解作用<ref name="deutsche-apotheker-zeitung.de">[https://www.deutsche-apotheker-zeitung.de/daz-az/1998/daz-43-1998/uid-4148 Zinkgluconat wirkt bei Kindern nicht], deutsche-apotheker-zeitung.de, abgerufen am 14. Februar 2016.</ref>。而在以[[成人|成人]]患者为实验对象的十项研究中，五项研究报告了[[锌|锌]]对[[感冒|感冒]]有积极缓解作用，但其他五项研究未发现其有效性<ref name="Webseite">{{cite web | url = http://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/o/cochrane/clsysrev/articles/CD001364/frame.html | title = Meenu Singh, Rashmi R. Das: Zinc for the common cold (Intervention Review) | accessdate = 2011-02-17 | publisher = The Cochrane Library | archive-date = 2011-02-19 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110219150305/http://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/o/cochrane/clsysrev/articles/CD001364/frame.html | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>[http://www.spiegel.de/wissenschaft/medizin/0,1518,745897,00.html ''Zink hilft bei Erkältungen''.] [[Spiegel_Online|Spiegel Online]], 16. Februar 2011.</ref>。在另一项[[對照實驗|对照研究]]中，通过[[鼻腔给药|鼻腔给药]]的葡萄糖酸锌对于[[鼻病毒|鼻病毒]]感染引起的感冒症状没有缓解作用；鼻腔滴入葡萄糖酸锌后，个别病例出现了永久性的[[嗅觉#嗅覺消失|嗅觉丧失]]<ref>[http://dgk.de/nc/gesundheit/mikronaehrstoffe/lexikon/mineralien/zink/therapie.html?sword_list%5B0%5D=zink Zink Therapie] Deutsches Grünes Kreuz für Gesundheit e. V., abgerufen am 16. Februar 2016.</ref><ref name="fda.gov">{{cite web|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090617182326/http://www.fda.gov/ForConsumers/ConsumerUpdates/ucm166931.htm|title=Warnings on Three Zicam Intranasal Zinc Products|date=2009-06-17|website=web.archive.org}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090617185322/http://www.fda.gov/NewsEvents/Newsroom/PressAnnouncements/ucm167065.htm|title=FDA Advises Consumers Not To Use Certain Zicam Cold Remedies|date=2009-06-17|website=web.archive.org}}</ref>。

